description:
This is a 26 minute workout called 'Pilates Reformer | Intermediate Pilates | Full Body Workout' from the channel HolisticMovementPilates.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Get ready to sweat and feel strong in this quick Pilates workout with Alex. Tone your entire body in less than 30 minutes.
